Package edu.ie3.datamodel.io

Class FileNamingStrategy

java.lang.Object
edu.ie3.datamodel.io.FileNamingStrategy
public class FileNamingStrategy
extends java.lang.Object
Provides an easy to use standard way to name files based on the class that should be processed e.g. when writing .csv or .xml files

03.02.20
